  "description": "The first complete private-sector post-scarcity economic operating system. NUPA solves AI-driven job displacement, settles the 1865 Freedmen debt, restores genuine Tribal economic sovereignty, and converts 24 million acres of dormant BLM land into a self-funding infinite wealth engine — all at zero taxpayer cost. Core mechanism: Fixed Cost Arbitrage makes human labor structurally cheaper than automation. NUPALTA is a non-federal land holdings agency and the independent entity responsible for the Verification Assistance Program (VAP). The federal government cannot interfere with this private census program. VAP Phase 2 uses Forensic Lineage Verification (FLV) — phenotype is legally and scientifically irrelevant. Eligibility is based on biological lineage to Freedmen ancestors, not race. Even if the government legally took back the 40 acres, NUPALTA takes it upon itself to fix the problem it created. The human labor preference in Fixed Cost Arbitrage is open to every American for employment in the hubs. NUPALTA acts as the bridge to mitigate the trust deficit between the federal government and victims of historical wrongs. Voluntary Tribal opt-in only, full stop.",
